So we have polled data using kafkaCOnnector to our topic{wikimedia.recentchange} in our kafka broker
now we want to perform some computations using this like count the no of times an email was created by a bot or human
This can be done using kafkas Stream application

What is kafka Streams?
Easy data processing and transformation library within kafka like data transformation,data enrichment,fraud detection,
monitoringand alerting
This can  be aeasily done using a standard java application , no need to write a separate cluster



